OL,3,CFarmer says changes to immigration
OL,4,Crules creates 'precarious' industry
OL,5,Cposition
OL,7,FA farmer in the south west of Scotland
OL,8,Fis warning that changes to immigration
OL,9,Frules have put the region's dairy
OL,10,Fsector in a "precarious" position.
OL,12,FRory Christie is a third generation
OL,13,Ffarmer based near Port William in
OL,14,FDumfries and Galloway.
OL,16,FHe says he is unable to recruit the
OL,17,Fskilled workers he needs locally and
OL,18,Ftherefore relies on employees from
OL,19,Foverseas to look after his herd, which
OL,20,Fsupplies milk for local cheese
OL,21,Fproducers.
OL,26,@rD@MOUrD@XO]
