OL,3,CFarmer says changes to immigration
OL,4,Crules creates 'precarious' industry
OL,5,Cposition
OL,7,FIn July, the UK Government removed
OL,8,F"farmer" 'from the skilled worker list
OL,9,Fof people, effectively blocking
OL,10,Foverseas recruitment. It is a move
OL,11,Fministers say will boost Britain's
OL,12,Fworkforce and reduce oversea reliance
OL,13,Fon workers.
OL,15,FSeven of the 15 employees on the farm
OL,16,Fare from overseas and six of them are
OL,17,Ffrom the Philippines.
OL,19,FHe said before they came, he was
OL,20,Fconsidering selling his herd.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@HO]
