OL,5,Cposition
OL,7,FRory said: "We couldn't look after
OL,8,Fthem properly, we couldn't get the
OL,9,Fperformance that we require. It's
OL,10,Fpretty difficult to make good money
OL,11,Ffrom dairy farming, you have to be
OL,12,Fexceptionally good at what you do
OL,13,Fwhich means you need exceptionally
OL,14,Fskilled people."
OL,16,FBenjie Yap came from the Philippines
OL,17,Fto work on Rory's farm three years ago.
