OL,7,FHe said: "Doing this kind of job,
OL,8,Fespecially dairy farming, you must
OL,9,Flove the job and you must be
OL,10,Fpassionate about it.
OL,12,F"The opportunity to come here and help
OL,13,Four families is really great, but the
OL,14,Fopportunity for the UK and Scottish
OL,15,Ffarmers to get the workers that they
OL,16,Fneed, that really will do the job for
OL,17,Fthem and excel, learn and have the
OL,18,Fknowledge to do everything that the
OL,19,Fbosses want us to do will be gone."
