OL,7,FThe National Farmers Union of Scotland
OL,8,Fsay they're "deeply concerned" about
OL,9,Fthe changes - warning that without
OL,10,Fskilled and willing workers,
OL,11,Fconfidence in the future of farming is
OL,12,Fat risk.
