OL,5,Cposition
OL,7,FGalloway MSP Finlay Carson said:
OL,8,F"There's over 25 dairy farms in
OL,9,FDumfries and Galloway that will be
OL,10,Fdirectly affected by this. They've now
OL,11,Fgot a tradition of getting a workforce
OL,12,Ffrom overseas and Labour's position on
OL,13,Fthe visa and the skilled labour list
OL,14,Fundermines what we're trying to do and
OL,15,Fputs food security as well as rural
OL,16,Fjobs at risk."
OL,26,@pD@AOU
