OL,3,CFarmer says changes to immigration
OL,4,Crules creates 'precarious' industry
OL,5,Cposition
OL,7,FA UK government spokesperson said:
OL,8,F"Fewer than 200 of this type of visa
OL,9,Fwere issued in the nine months before
OL,10,Fit was removed. It is essential we
OL,11,Fbuild a more resilient homegrown
OL,12,Fworkforce and reduce reliance on
OL,13,Foverseas labour.
OL,15,F"The government recognises the vital
OL,16,Fcontribution skilled workers make to
OL,17,Fthe UK's agricultural sector and is
OL,18,Fensuring the immigration system
OL,19,Fsupports this in a way that aligns
OL,20,Fwith the development of domestic
OL,21,Fskills."
